Kan semua nya dari Ilahi
Kan kita yang mohon di bukakan jalan, dibukakan hati
Usah diragukan segenap rasa,
Usah curiga segenap takdir
Kan yang memberi kan segenap rasa,

Doug (Jack Black) and Griff (Paul Rudd) have been best friends since they were kids, and have always dreamed of remaking their all-time favorite movie: the cinematic "classic" Anaconda. When a midlife crisis pushes them to finally go for it, they head deep into the Amazon to start filming. But things get real when an actual giant anaconda appears, turning their comically chaotic movie set into a deadly situation. The movie they’re dying to make? It might just get them killed

Terus doakanmu

#TheHousemaidMovie

THE HOUSEMAID is a wildly entertaining thriller starring Sydney Sweeney and Amanda Seyfried, based on the best-selling book. From director Paul Feig, the film plunges audiences into a twisted world where perfection is an illusion, and nothing is as it seems. Trying to escape her past, Millie (Sweeney) accepts a job as a live-in housemaid for the wealthy Nina (Seyfried) and Andrew Winchester (Brandon Sklenar). But what begins as a dream job quickly unravels into something far more dangerous – a sexy, seductive game of secrets, scandal, and power. Behind the Winchesters’ closed doors lies a world of shocking twists that will leave you guessing until the very end.

snippet.description:

Lyrics:

[Chorus: Adam Levine & (R. City)]
If I got locked away
And we lost it all today
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?
If I showed you my flaws
If I couldn't be strong
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?
Right about now

[Verse 1: R. City]
If a judge 'for life' me, would ya stay by my side?
Or is you gonna say goodbye?
Can you tell me right now?
If I couldn't buy you the fancy things in life
Shawty, would it be alright?
Come on, show me that you are down

[Pre-Chorus: R. City]
Now tell me, would you really ride for me?
(Would you really ride for me?)
Baby, tell me, would you die for me?
(Tell me, would you die for me?)
Would you spend your whole life with me? (Wassup)
Would you be there to always hold me down?
Tell me, would you really cry for me?
(Would you really cry for me?)
Baby, don't lie to me (Baby, don't lie to me)
If I didn't have anything (Wassup)
I wanna know, would you stick around?

[Chorus: Adam Levine]
If I got locked away
And we lost it all today
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?
If I showed you my flaws
If I couldn't be strong
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?

[Verse 2: R. City]
Skiddly dong, dong, dong, dang
All I want is somebody real, who don't need much
A gyal I know that I can trust
To be here when money low
If I did not have nothing else to give but love
Would that even be enough? (Tell me, tell me, tell me)
Gyal me need fi know, aha

[Pre-Chorus: R. City]
Now tell me, would you really ride for me?
(Would you really ride for me?)
Baby, tell me, would you die for me?
(Tell me, would you die for me?)
Would you spend your whole life with me? (Wassup)
Would you be there to always hold me down?
Tell me, would you really cry for me?
(Would you really cry for me?)
Baby, don't lie to me (Baby, don't lie to me)
If I didn't have anything (Wassup)
I wanna know, would you stick around?

[Chorus: Adam Levine]
If I got locked away
And we lost it all today
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?
If I showed you my flaws
If I couldn't be strong
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?

[Bridge: R. City]
Tell me, tell me, would you want me? (Want me)
Tell me, tell me, would you call me? (Call me)
If you knew I wasn't balling
'Cause I need a gyal who's always by my side
Tell me, tell me, do you need me? (Need me)
Tell me, tell me, do you love me? (Yeah)
Or is you just tryna play me?
'Cause I need a gyal to hold me down for life

[Chorus: Adam Levine]
If I got locked away
And we lost it all today
Tell me honestly would you still love me the same?
If I showed you my flaws
If I couldn't be strong
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?
If I got locked away
And we lost it all today
Tell me honestly would you still love me the same?
If I showed you my flaws
If I couldn't be strong
Tell me honestly, would you still love me the same?

[Outro: Adam Levine]
Would you still love me the same?

Lirik Risalah Cinta - Syam

Andai ku dapat undurkan masa, 
Kan ku ubah coretan risalah cinta,
Kerana ku tahu diriku tak sempurna,
Teganya dirimu berubah arah,
Hilanglah cinta di dalam gelita, 

Andai ku dapat menggapai awan, 
Kan ku perlihatkan keindahan cinta,
Ku Sirami cinta yang bersulam dusta, 
Engkau berubah menghilang arah,
Kuterima andai ini suratannya, 
Oh...sayang

Andai dapat ke undurkan satu waktu, 
Kan ku ubah Coretan cinta yang Baru,
Ku Hiasi dengan permata syurgawi, 
Agar cinta kita lebih bersinar lagi, 

Hancur hati ini berderai harapan, 
Kerna diri ini banyak kekurangan,
Demi kerana mu rela ku lepaskan, 
Semoga dirimu gapai kebahagiaan,

Andai ku dapat menggapai awan, 
Kan ku perlihatkan keindahan cinta,
Ku Sirami cinta yang bersulam dusta, 
Engkau berubah menghilang arah,
Hilang lah Cinta Di Dalam Gelita, 
Oh..

snippet.title: DIOR大穎 - LOUISE - (Official MV）
snippet.description:
今天是我們認識的第三個月
I wrote a song for my friend👭



This is a simple story I’d like to share with all of you！

Back in June this year, when I wasn’t in the best place emotionally, I went to London to study. 
That’s where I met a classmate （LOUISE）
who unexpectedly became a very close friend.

We only spent three weeks together,
but it felt like fate — as if she was an angel sent to remind me
that the world is so much bigger, with so many things worth chasing.
So, I wrote this song to remember that time, 
to celebrate the moment I found clarity in myself, 
and to treasure every encounter that leads to the next meeting.

Because our English wasn’t great, that’s why we ended up in the same class in London HAHAHAH
We even promised to go to Australia next year for two more months of English lessons together, to keep growing into better versions of ourselves！

That’s also why this is the very first English song I’ve ever written 
I really using up all the vocabulary I know, haha.

Anyways! Thank you so much for listening to my music and my story.
My name is Dior, and I’m a singer-songwriter from Malaysia,Johor,Batu Pahat,Rengit. 
I’M A KAMPUNG GIRL!

I never imagined myself
stepping into the world of English songs.

But maybe… that’s what life is about.
You’ll never know where the road takes you
unless you keep moving forward.

So, whatever you’re going through,
let the wind carry you onward. ✨




《Louise》
作詞：DIOR大穎
作曲：DIOR大穎
演唱：DIOR大穎、LOUISE

I met an angel
Oh her name is Louise
She’s only just turned eighteen
Oh she’s still chasing her dream

It’s not easy to find a friendship like this
Even though we only had a few weeks
But it still means a lot to me

Ohh girl, you don’t know how much you healed me
You woke a part I couldn’t see
You never know
You never know
You let me be 

We said goodbye till we meet again
And said goodbye but it’s not the end
Said goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
All the little things with you I won’t forget

Let me tell you a secret
We don’t care what you think
Maybe we got a little crazy
But life is still young
We‘re born to be free

Take it easy
Try to live it wild and free
Sometimes life - a little hazy
So maybe just let it be

Oh girl, you don’t know how much you healed me
You woke a part I couldn’t see
You never know
you never know
你讓我成為自己

We said goodbye till we meet again
And said goodbye but it’s not the end
Said goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
All the little things with you I won’t forget

Goodbye till we meet again
And said goodbye but it’s not the end
Said goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
All the little things with you I won’t forget

Let‘s say goodbye till we meet again
And say goodbye but it’s not the end
Say goodbye, remember us this way
Till the end
Day by day we stay the same
See you again

snippet.title: DRX vs. NRG — VALORANT Champions Paris — Group Stage
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:

For the first time, Chainsaw Man slashes his way onto the big screen in an epic, action-fueled adventure that continues the hugely popular anime series. Denji worked as a Devil Hunter for the yakuza, trying to pay off the debt he inherited from his parents, until the yakuza betrayed him and had him killed. As he was losing consciousness, Denji’s beloved chainsaw-powered devil-dog, Pochita, made a deal with Denji and saved his life. This fused the two together, creating the unstoppable Chainsaw Man. Now, in a brutal war between devils, hunters, and secret enemies, a mysterious girl named Reze has stepped into his world, and Denji faces his deadliest battle yet, fueled by love in a world where survival knows no rules.

悪魔の心臓を持つ「チェンソーマン」となり、公安対魔特異４課に所属するデビルハンターの少年・デンジ（戸谷菊之介）。
憧れのマキマ（楠木ともり）とのデートで浮かれている中、急な雨に見舞われ、
雨宿りしていると偶然“レゼ”（上田麗奈）という少女と出会った。
近所のカフェで働いているという彼女はデンジに優しく微笑み、二人は急速に親密に。
この出会いを境に、デンジの日常は変わり始めていく……

For the first time, Chainsaw Man slashes his way onto the big screen in an epic, action-fueled adventure that continues the hugely popular anime series. Denji worked as a Devil Hunter for the yakuza, trying to pay off the debt he inherited from his parents, until the yakuza betrayed him and had him killed. As he was losing consciousness, Denji’s beloved chainsaw-powered devil-dog, Pochita, made a deal with Denji and saved his life. This fused the two together, creating the unstoppable Chainsaw Man. Now, in a brutal war between devils, hunters, and secret enemies, a mysterious girl named Reze has stepped into his world, and Denji faces his deadliest battle yet, fueled by love in a world where survival knows no rules.

snippet.description:

우기 (YUQI) 1st Single [Motivation]
Pre-Save https://YUQI.lnk.to/Motivation

Composed by 우기, 우석, Siixk Jun
Lyrics by 우기, 우석
Arranged by Siixk Jun

=======

[Lyrics]

아프다
날카로운 기억 속에 혼자 차갑다
눈물아 흘러 빗방울

아프다
즐겨 듣던 노래가 쏟아졌고
또다시 나만 아프다
내가 너보다 못되게 할걸 그땐

또다시 찾아오는 아침에 내가 없어도
안기며 웃던 날 기억 못 해도
아프긴 하지만 괜찮아 너니까
You know I’ll always be with you, baby

더 깊어져 가는 밤안개 속 그 길 위에서
혹시 우리가 서로를 잃어도
날 사랑했던 널 찾아갈 테니까
You know I’ll always be with you, baby

너가 먼저 날 떠나버렸지
“그만하자.” 아무 표정 없이
이제 알았어 그때 왜 그랬는지
반쯤 미쳐 너의 이름을 불렀는데

I can’t hear what you’re saying
돌아와 줘 내게 너도 미쳐있었던 내게
You’re breaking my heart
(I don’t know why you did this to me)

또다시 찾아오는 아침에 내가 없어도
안기며 웃던 날 기억 못 해도
아프긴 하지만 괜찮아 너니까
You know I’ll always be with you, baby

더 깊어져 가는 밤안개 속 그 길 위에서
혹시 우리가 서로를 또 잃어도
날 사랑했던 널 찾아갈 테니까
You know I’ll always be with you, baby

난 아프다
참 아프다
또 아프다
You know I’ll always be with you, baby

I’m falling apart
My love is gone
I’m breaking down
우리 어디서 언제든 행복하기를 바라
